visualization_settings.text:
New user is a user who made first transaction in period
Old user - user who made transactions before the period with new transaction

card.description:
new is the user who made the first transaction this week and all his transactions this week
old - all other users
card.name: Turnover OOR weekly by new and old users

native.query:
WITH min_cr_date as (
    select USER_ID, date_trunc({{granularity}} ,min(CREATED_AT)) as min_cr_dt
        from MART.TRANSACTIONS
        where CONFIRMED and
              SOURCE_MAIN = 'widget' and
              TYPE_MAIN in  ('buy', 'sell')
        group by 1
)

select date_trunc({{granularity}}, TRANSACTIONS.CREATED_AT) as dt_week
     , case when date_trunc({{granularity}}, TRANSACTIONS.CREATED_AT) = date_trunc({{granularity}}, min_cr_dt)
         then 'new user'
         else 'old user' end as type_user
     , sum(TURNOVER_EUR) as sum_turnover_EUR
    from MART.TRANSACTIONS 
inner join min_cr_date on min_cr_date.USER_ID = TRANSACTIONS.USER_ID
where TRANSACTIONS.CONFIRMED and
      TRANSACTIONS.TYPE_MAIN in ('buy', 'sell') and
      TRANSACTIONS.SOURCE_MAIN = 'widget' and
      {{CREATED_AT}} and
      {{partner_name}} and
      {{widget_id}} and 
      {{is_reccurring}}
group by 1,2
order by 1,2

native.query:
